<h1>Ryan Koriya</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://www.ryankoriya.com/#!now/c24yq">ryankoriya.com/#!now/c24yq</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
London
England
United Kingdom
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Singer-Songwriter-Producer
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
A sonic physician, creating Passion-Pop then administering it straight to your heart with a voice that's both soothing and uplifting.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I make music to help sooth emotional wounds in others just like it's done for me from day one and still does today. Sharing is caring!
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
Imagine it's a year from now. You know that thing you've always wanted to do?  For example, learn a new language. Well, meet two current versions of yourself: V1 still speaks only English. V2 already has a year's experience in speaking French! Which version do you want to be?! The key is to just make a start... No excuses!
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
'7 Strange Questions That Help You Find Your Life Purpose' by Mark Manson: <a href="http://markmanson.net/life-purpose">http://markmanson.net/life-purpose</a>
</p>

